{"tid":200825,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞寫錯鄭松泰做「鄭屎」　港台認衰致歉","createTime":"2017-04-14T09:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T11:28:17.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8021d2d612ab7b4214cb8fd9b87a795646b2f350","tid":200825,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"警方正式落案起訴熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰侮辱國旗及區旗罪，香港電台在網頁報道該則新聞時，在第一句竟將鄭松泰的姓名寫錯為「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鄭屎</span></span>」，但第二句則正確寫為「鄭松泰」。港台其後發現出錯作出更正，但有關錯字畫面已被眼利網民複製，並放上社交網站分享。<br />\n<br />\n港台發言人回覆東網查詢時證實出錯，聲稱電台新聞部把已作報道的新聞上載至網站時出現「亂碼」，發現後已即時更正，並向鄭松泰道歉，鄭已接受該台道歉。港台已責成同事今後要小心處理。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n鄭屎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61262b52249d8c52a8234a8f4f04f153b074ac77","tid":200825,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2883438ce57aadab862a5339d8354028a9fc0eeb","tid":200825,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主係傻鳩"},{"pid":"6f7c0a0ffce7b11af1cfda41cd4d7284ae639e66","tid":200825,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"@賓科"},{"pid":"6a1f79e7ab6125a020090cd6ee679d27b69bd0d2","tid":200825,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"